trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement3D" /> types to UI Automation.

By default, any class that inherits from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> uses <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer> to communicate with [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 기본적으로 모든 클래스에서 상속 되 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> 사용 하 여 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer> 통신할 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: If you create a class that inherits from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>, you may want to provide an automation peer to support the functionality of your class.
trans-unit.target: 상속 되는 클래스를 만들면 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>, 클래스의 기능을 지원 하도록 자동화 피어를 제공 하는 것이 좋습니다.

trans-unit.source: Override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> method to return a string that represents the type of the element associated with the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer>.
trans-unit.target: 재정의 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> 요소와 연관 된 형식을 나타내는 문자열을 반환 하는 메서드는 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer>합니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you create a class called `My3DElement` and an automation peer called `My3DElementAutomationPeer`, override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> method to return the string "My3DElement".
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어, 라는 클래스를 만들면 `My3DElement` 라는 자동화 피어와 `My3DElementAutomationPeer`, 재정의 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetClassNameCore%2A> "My3DElement" 문자열을 반환 하는 메서드.

trans-unit.source: If your class matches one of the known control types, override the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A> method to return that <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>.
trans-unit.target: 알려진된 컨트롤 형식 중 하 나와 일치 하는 클래스, 재정의 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlTypeCore%2A> 메서드를 사용 하는 반환 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Note that although the existing <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> values are generally associated with 2D controls, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> indicates a control's functionality, not its appearance.
trans-unit.target: 하지만 기존 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> 값은 일반적으로 2D 컨트롤과 연결 된 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType> 모양이 아닌 컨트롤의 기능을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: So if your <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> invokes an action when the user clicks it, you probably want <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetHelpTextCore%2A> to return <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 따라서 프로그램 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> 사용자가 클릭할 싶을 때 작업을 호출 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer.GetHelpTextCore%2A> 반환할 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The behavior of your custom <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> determines what other methods you should override.
trans-unit.target: 사용자 지정 동작 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> 를 재정의 해야 하는 방법을 결정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Each method topic in the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer> describes how the method is used and when it is appropriate to override it.
trans-unit.target: 각 메서드 항목에는 <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElement3DAutomationPeer> 고 메서드를 사용 하는 방법 및 재정의에 적합 한 경우에 대해 설명 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A content element contains data that is presented to the user.
trans-unit.target: 콘텐츠 요소는 사용자에 게 표시 되는 데이터를 포함 합니다.

trans-unit.source: An example of a content element is an item in a list box or a button on a dialog box.

trans-unit.source: You typically use non-content elements, which are also called peripheral elements, to manipulate the content in a composite control.
trans-unit.target: 일반적으로 복합 컨트롤의 콘텐츠를 조작 하기 위한 주변 요소 라고도 하는 비 콘텐츠 요소를 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: An example of a non-content element is the button on a drop-down control.
trans-unit.target: 콘텐츠가 아닌 요소의 예에는 드롭다운 목록 컨트롤에서 단추입니다.
